name: John Warne
description: '''John Warne''' is an American musician who has been active since 1996. He is best known for being the bassist for the [[Christian rock]] band [[Relient K]] as well as being a founding member of the [[Christian punk]] [[band (music)|band]] [[Ace Troubleshooter]]. His hometown is [[Minneapolis, Minnesota]], and he now lives in [[Golden, Colorado]].
